  "privacyPolicyTitle": "개인정보 Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: March 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your 개인정보 is paramount. This 개인정보 Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
