  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns 정보 this 개인정보 Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • E이메일 privacy@vitalseker.com • S지원 support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to 전체 privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
